//dstatic.zuimeia.com/media/article/image/2016/6/27/efed3faf-30f3-4edc-a1df-166227c3d780_800x532.jpeg\"/><\/p><p><img src=\"http://dstatic.zuimeia.com/media/article/image/2016/6/27/34b3bc7f-20e6-497b-b2ee-f23c472fc642_800x533.jpeg\"/><\/p><p><!--?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"no\"?-->给看背面还不怎么了解其酷炫程度的你，它的正面是这样的：<\/p><p><img src=\"http://dstatic.zuimeia.com/media/article/image/2016/6/27/4746043c-40a3-45a1-aae4-d067986fb14f_614x699.jpeg\"/><\/p><p><!--?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"no\"?-->是不是「哇哦」！另外，Adidas 为 Y-3 Sports 拍的广告片也是相当炫，让男女模特在布满砂石的山地上打滚儿奔跑，来告诉你这衣服鞋子多么酷儿。<\/p><p><img src=\"http://dstatic.zuimeia.com/media/article/image/2016/6/27/414df079-1394-4432-8054-8d82d024b4b5_800x337.jpeg\"/><\/p>","web_url":"http://design.zuimeia.com/article/38/","image_url":"http://dstatic.zuimeia.com/common/image/2016/6/27/2ddebe31-507a-44a0-a0ca-847260e27f77_470x470.jpeg","like_user_num":283,"publish_at":1467033480000,"id":38}]}
